Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.58,0:00:13.36,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Underwater combat honors\N the god of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:18.60,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,In times of great need, the men of this island\Nhave long proven their resolve in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:23.39,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,If you are truly prepared, \Nyou'll have to prove it, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:07.66,Flashback,Hairi,0,0,0,,Let's do everything we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:14.50,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs20\shad0\bord1\blur1\pos(320,300)\c&HFFF1E5&\3c&H7F5B53&}Is that all you've got, son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.01,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:22.43,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.89,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs20\shad0\bord1\blur1\pos(320,300)\c&HFFF1E5&\3c&H7F5B53&}This is it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.21,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs20\shad0\bord1\blur1\pos(320,300)\c&HFFF1E5&\3c&H7F5B53&}You've never even seen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.92,Default,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\fs20\shad0\bord1\blur1\pos(320,300)\c&HFFF1E5&\3c&H7F5B53&}what she's like when she's alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:37.74,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hairi! You got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.53,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:46.16,Main - Italics,Kobato,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.42,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,He threw him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.50,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,He won!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.72,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,Hairi won!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:23.66,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, Shiroha \Nlost both of her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.66,0:03:27.29,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,She's been closed off ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.86,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Never made many friends.\NHad terrible rumors spread about her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.38,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,She's been forced to spend her summers alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.04,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.15,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.49,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'll be by her side during \Nthe Natsudori ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.05,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'll protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:49.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That ought to dispel the silly rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.47,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hairi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.81,0:03:57.91,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:03.59,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,The priestess in the Natsudori ritual \Nmay only be accompanied by family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:07.58,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Family...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:13.08,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,N-N-N-N-No way. That can't be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:17.17,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hairi and me... m-m-m-m-married?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.30,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,Naturally, it would be entirely symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.51,0:04:27.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I owe Shiroha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:28.76,Default,Kobato,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:35.14,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So if she's going to be in danger,\N I want to be by her side to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:38.77,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:43.03,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,If it isn't a bother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.36,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.37,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Please be my spouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.50,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:01.42,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,You two are getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:03.33,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's just an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:07.77,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,You're going to be busy \Nwith the butterfly covenant and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.47,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,so don't worry about the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.84,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Break a leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:13.73,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.44,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:33.71,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,We'll be lighting them and sending them\N off to sea the day of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.79,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,Don't forget to bring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.16,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:42.00,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,The red lights Shiroha says \Nshe saw were these lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:45.13,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey, Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.05,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:46.87,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.84,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Hotta-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:54.14,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Her mother fell ill, and last winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.25,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hotta-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:04.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Do you know what Obon is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.22,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:10.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's the one time of year \Nthe dead come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:14.03,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,The dead come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:16.70,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.75,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I didn't mean you can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:26.81,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Anyway, they return on the night \Nof the Natsudori ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.39,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's scary to go out in the dark, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:31.94,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:36.64,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,That's why we have to light\Nthe way for them with these lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.14,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So they feel safe on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:46.90,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.64,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,You have a dress rehearsal today, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.61,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.16,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha should be there by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:56.42,Default,Tenzen,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:07:01.31,Default,Tenzen,0,0,0,,According to her vision, \Nyou two are drowning, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.33,Default,Tenzen,0,0,0,,Could it be because you're\N in those kimonos in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:06.09,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:13.93,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,About the kimono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.47,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,How do I get it off of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.85,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Why would you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:24.40,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll be able to \Nwhen the time comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.03,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,What time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.02,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,H-Have you lost your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:33.66,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Th-The covenant isn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.23,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to lose it\Nif you fall in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:41.83,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Not even a kappa could swim in that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:44.22,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.09,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,But don't you mean a hippo ({\i1}kaba{\i0})?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.74,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:55.43,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I was just trying to make\N a little wordplay joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:03.48,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Either way, you're right.\N I can't swim in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.67,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.14,0:08:08.82,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Ryoichi and Tenzen pointed it out to me,\Nso I figured I should consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:11.82,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I'll consider it too, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:13.92,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hairi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.41,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.33,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,For thinking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.87,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,For everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.78,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:34.99,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Katou residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:37.04,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hi, Nomiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.47,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.98,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.98,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Isn't the priestess supposed \Nto cloister herself in the hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:47.37,Main - Italics,Miki,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:50.42,Main - Italics,Miki,0,0,0,,But Ao's pretending to be her for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.54,Main - Italics,Miki,0,0,0,,Ryoichi and Tenzen are looking for Shiroha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:54.49,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.19,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'll look for her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.93,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I have an idea where she might be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.78,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Everyone's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.64,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You could've at least told someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.24,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:19.84,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I just really wanted to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:24.02,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,The closer we get to the Natsudori ritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:26.25,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,the more vivid it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:30.19,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I can see your face clearly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.20,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Why did you talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:39.63,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Then you took me places...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.38,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I should have been alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.84,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I don't mind going away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:50.25,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,But I can't stand the thought of losing \Nsomeone I care about again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:59.55,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm still glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You being here saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:08.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,So please don't talk like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone feels the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:13.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,None of us could stand losing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:20.20,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.16,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.37,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I don't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:24.83,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:31.63,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We should get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.77,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:35.85,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.06,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I want you to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.38,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:49.52,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.26,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Sea fireflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.19,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sea fireflies...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Fireflies in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:11:01.78,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,This is a secret place my father\N showed me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:04.50,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,They haven't glowed since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:08.25,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,But they're glowing again this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:09.87,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,It's been ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.04,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.96,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I must be lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:18.48,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:23.39,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,There was a time I wanted\N to go into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Into the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:28.11,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I guess I got tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:31.98,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I wanted to speed up time\Nand see them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:35.56,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why I wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.09,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Do you still want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:44.44,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,There's no telling how long it'd take.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.76,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,So I'm good now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.62,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:05.14,Default,All,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.08,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:25.82,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord1\fnArial\fs18\b1\fay.03\move(550.969,118.493,70.969,118.493)\c&HE9DEDA&\3c&H523F42&}Welcome to Torishirojima Island
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:25.82,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord1\fnArial\fs14\b1\fay.01\move(560.969,275,80.969,275)\c&H8EDACC&\3c&H5F6555&}Thanks for visiting Torishirojima
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.20,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\fs14\fay-.07\fax.1\bord1\fnArial\b1\move(335.36,202.095,640.36,202.095)\c&H33293A&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H6228D7&}SAUSAGES
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.20,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs14\fay-.07\fax.1\bord1\fnArial\b1\move(125.36,222.095,430.36,222.095)\c&H593EF2&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H6228D7&}GRILLED SQUID
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.20,Default,Text,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs14\fay-.07\fax.1\bord1\fnArial\b1\move(-75.36,250.095,230.36,250.095)\c&H593EF2&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H6228D7&}YAKISOBA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.50,Default,Kyouko,0,0,0,,Say hi to your wife for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:33.53,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.38,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I've gotten so used to this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:54.12,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,a rainbow-colored butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:16.67,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Umi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:19.53,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.46,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.20,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I was chasing a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.98,0:13:26.84,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,And what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.45,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Just taking a little walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.55,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.55,0:13:31.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.49,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shall we go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.82,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.34,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,I wanna walk around a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.66,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.54,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,It's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:46.59,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.17,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I ran into someone I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.46,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,Just hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:51.38,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,You have to finish the butterfly covenant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:53.29,Default,Miki,0,0,0,,or we can't start the Natsudori ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.04,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:06.30,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,We hereby begin the butterfly covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:46.88,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.18,Default,Men,0,0,0,,Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.71,0:14:58.34,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,We carried that boat last year too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.24,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,but I swear it's getting heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:02.77,Default,Tenzen,0,0,0,,It must get heavier\Nthe more wishes it carries.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.66,0:15:05.27,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.06,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,Looks like nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.35,Default,Tenzen,0,0,0,,Good for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:14.66,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:17.43,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,Lucky break we finished\N before it started, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.94,Default,Tenzen,0,0,0,,Too bad we won't get to see\N the lanterns off,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.29,Default,Tenzen,0,0,0,,but we should head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.09,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:27.07,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Have you seen Hotta-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.63,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.47,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,We can't find her anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:33.59,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Nomiki's calling for her on the PA.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:36.20,Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Catch her if you find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:38.52,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hairi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.96,0:15:41.23,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,The future I saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:45.15,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,With you and me in the water, yeah? \NBut everything's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.27,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I just saw it clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:51.82,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,The other person I thought I saw... \NIt was a little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.12,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Was it Hotta-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.32,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But why's she in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:15:59.95,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.45,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,She's on the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We have to bring her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:05.99,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.04,Default,Ryoichi; Tenzen,0,0,0,,Hey! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:11.88,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where are you, Hotta-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:15.98,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,Dad's gonna smack me later\Nfor taking the boat without telling him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:17.64,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,You'd better be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:20.31,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.13,0:16:22.40,Default,Ryoichi,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hotta-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:27.31,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,Onii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.18,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.94,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,I thought I could see my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:36.90,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,I thought this boat would take me to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:37.87,Default,Hotta,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:40.46,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Give me your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.48,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.12,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hairi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.09,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.06,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:04.03,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Ryoichi, take Hotta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:11.02,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:13.40,Main - Italics,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hairi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:17.74,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.06,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.25,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,No... that's not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.94,Main - Italics,Shiroha,0,0,0,,We are the weavers of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:41.22,Main - Italics,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Seek as you may, stranger,\Nit will be futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:44.69,Main - Italics,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Even if you meet this summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.13,Main - Italics,Shiroha,0,0,0,,that is all it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.91,Main - Italics,Shiroha,0,0,0,,We shall simply continue to weave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:55.88,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:56.78,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Which way do I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:01.43,Main - Italics,Hairi,0,0,0,,Is that....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:06.04,Main - Italics,Umi,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.80,Main - Italics,Umi,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:49.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.09,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Thank you for all you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:55.54,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:57.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,We both did a good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:21.92,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,There's something \NI've been wanting to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:25.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The first time I laid eyes on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.12,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hairi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:31.37,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I knew you were swimming \Nin your underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.34,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Sorry I never said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:47.89,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Why would you tell me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:51.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I mean, there was so much \Ngoing on. I was overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:54.98,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I have no idea what to say right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:20:00.28,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,A-A-A-A-And {\i1}that's{\i0} what you chose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.10,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:04.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm such a dosukoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.06,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:14.72,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,The future is as dark as that sea was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.19,0:20:17.76,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Normally, there's no way \Nto see what's ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:23.17,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,But you cast a ray of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.51,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I think that's your real power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:32.64,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Isn't that awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:37.61,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Shiroha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.64,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,N-N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:40.59,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.20,0:20:43.37,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Just something I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.51,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.16,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Was it something ominous again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.81,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:51.16,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,It wasn't ominous at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.38,0:21:08.58,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.23,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.23,0:21:12.33,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Remembered what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:14.85,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,How to spend summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:20.07,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,How did I ever forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:22.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It's such a simple, basic thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:27.36,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I remembered that I love summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:29.30,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Hai—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:30.99,Main - Italics,Ferry Announcement,0,0,0,,We will be departing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:33.58,Main - Italics,Ferry Announcement,0,0,0,,To all passengers, please complete boarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:42.00,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,There's two things \NI want to say before I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:44.30,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:45.98,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:50.68,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,It was brief, but I had fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:56.68,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I had fun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:00.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Also, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.04,0:22:03.91,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I've fallen in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.62,0:22:28.26,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,Shiroha?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:35.60,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:39.52,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:43.86,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I've fallen in love with you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:47.69,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'll come back to this island—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:51.79,Main - Italics,Ferry Announcement,0,0,0,,Due to technical difficulties, \Nwe will be turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:22:56.69,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,Why are you coming back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:03.86,Default,Hairi,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:06.09,Default,Shiroha,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:27.55,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Next time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:30.05,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,Next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.40,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,What do I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:36.86,Default,Umi,0,0,0,,What am I...?

